s one is gonna show a different level of maturity with his lyrics and with my music.\\\"\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"a different level\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"maturity\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"his lyrics\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"my music\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like this is some of the best music I have done in my career,\\\" saidThe Chroniclegend.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best music\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, the pairstopped byJimmy Kimmel Live!and spoke about working together onMissionary.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Kimmel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.993877568662241e-23, \"text\": \"Kimmel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Kimmel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Kimmel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first album I have done with Snoop was in 1993 and it's the only album I have ever produced on Snoop,\\\" Dr. Dre said at the time.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first album\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"Snoop\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the only album\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"Snoop\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr. Dre\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\